### Get all courses
GET http://localhost:5001/api/courses

### Create a new course
POST http://localhost:5001/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teacher_id": "<uuid>",
  "title": "Python 101",
  "description": "Intro to Python",
  "is_published": true
}

### Get a course by ID
GET http://localhost:5001/api/courses/<uuid>
